{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1782251458243,"sessionID":"ses_1098975a8ffeiBixvx5sVB9TOn","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"433767062","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/private/tmp/tokenwarden-bench/2026-06-23T16-47-14-546Z/tokenwarden-docs-from-code-2/repo/bench-artifacts/cache-api.md","content":"# Cache API\n\nThe cache API provides a simple key-value cache implementation with basic CRUD operations.\n\n## createCache()\n\nCreates and returns a new cache instance. The cache uses an internal `Map` to store values.\n\n```js\nimport { createCache } from './cache'\n\nconst cache = createCache()\n```\n\n## Methods\n\n### get(key)\n\nRetrieves a value from the cache by key.\n\n- **Params**: `key` - The key to look up\n- **Returns**: The value associated with the key, or `undefined` if not found\n\n### set(key, value)\n\nStores a value in the cache.\n\n- **Params**: `key` - The key to store under, `value` - The value to store\n- **Returns**: The stored value\n\n### delete(key)\n\nRemoves a value from the cache.\n\n- **Params**: `key` - The key to delete\n- **Returns**: `true` if the key existed and was removed, `false` otherwise\n\n### clear()\n\nRemoves all entries from the cache.\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/private/tmp/tokenwarden-bench/2026-06-23T16-47-14-546Z/tokenwarden-docs-from-code-2/repo/bench-artifacts/cache-api.md","exists":false,"truncated":false,"tokenwarden":{"wouldHaveUsedTokens":6,"usedTokens":6,"savedTokens":0,"percentSaved":0,"rawPath":"/tmp/tokenwarden-bench/2026-06-23T16-47-14-546Z/tokenwarden-docs-from-code-2/tokenwarden/encrypted/raw-tool-output/ses_1098975a8ffeiBixvx5sVB9TOn/433767062.txt.enc","event":{"timestamp":"2026-06-23T21:50:58.212Z","sessionID":"ses_1098975a8ffeiBixvx5sVB9TOn","source":"tool-output","label":"write","wouldHaveUsedTokens":6,"usedTokens":6,"savedTokens":0,"percentSaved":0,"metadata":{"callID":"433767062","rawPath":"/tmp/tokenwarden-bench/2026-0